{"tid":1884861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"英妹翻唱少女時代前輩FANS SONG比人鬧爆","createTime":"2020-02-18T01:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T09:37:58.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb830c8b5eed8cdab9f56ae7c4d910f1f382fca","tid":1884861,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"韓國女團IZ*ONE原定去年11月推出首張正規專輯《BLOOM*IZ》，但受《PRODUCE 101》系列造馬醜聞影響，IZ*ONE暫停手上工作，而《BLOOM*IZ》延遲至今天（17日）才正式面世。回歸在即，IZ*ONE最年少成員張員瑛（又譯：張元英）憑歌寄意，向苦等了3個月的WIZ*ONE（IZ*ONE粉絲）衷心致謝。<br />\n<br />\n張員瑛昨晚（15日）透過社交平台分享翻唱少女時代2016年推出，慶祝出道9周年的單曲《那夏天（0805）》片段，並表示：「我們相見的一天，苦惱很久該說甚麼話，所以準備了小禮物，這首歌是非常尊敬的少女時代前輩名為《那夏天》的歌曲，想着WIZ*ONE所以唱了這歌。WIZ*ONE，真心感謝你們！」<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE回歸在即，張員瑛翻唱少女時代的歌曲表達謝意。（IG/@official_izone）<br />\n<br />\n張員瑛翻唱的《那夏天》可透過Facebook和Twitter收聽。（Facebook/@official.izone）<br />\n<br />\n雖然去年檢察院指出，《PRODUCE 48》節目組在決賽前已經決定IZ*ONE出道人選，換言之，IZ*ONE成員不是按《PRODUCE 101》系列規定，經國民投票選出，但WIZ*ONE仍力撐IZ*ONE，發表聲明支持IZ*ONE繼續活動，今次張員瑛翻唱歌曲，是為了感謝過去三個月WIZ*ONE對IZ*ONE不離不棄。<br />\n<br />\n雖然IZ*ONE陷入造馬風波，WIZ*ONE仍對IZ*ONE不離不棄。（Twitter/@KCON_Global）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u2Yn4k6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu2Yn4k6.jpg&h=cc12d0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tNXdtns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtNXdtns.jpg&h=bd096e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M1GCHjm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM1GCHjm.jpg&h=b234841d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oQ1hECw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoQ1hECw.jpg&h=c8d05c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SZ7XAAs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSZ7XAAs.jpg&h=ca3a5eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u4tG2gI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu4tG2gI.jpg&h=89e26450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8aL44kj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8aL44kj.jpg&h=8232f576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3359a8d7c28dbeb92d9eb252f85fda38537ed86","tid":1884861,"uid":555,"like":16,"dislike":34,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"sone麻撚煩"},{"pid":"2e0d6a0856ebf70a4200ebbc58b7e7409caec0e5","tid":1884861,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"唱首歌都俾人鬧😅"},{"pid":"4db219c377e19fac0529a0bf364eaddfa5e4e7db","tid":1884861,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"噓 jollyhsu: sone玻璃心？！先搞清楚0805對sone是什麼意義吧，不要動別人的fan song很難嗎<br />\n噓 samliusam: 對自己的粉絲唱別人家的fansong有事嗎<br />\n&rarr; EVA1125ONCE: 對自己粉絲唱別人家的粉絲頌蠻好笑的<br />\n噓 Leonieee: 唱別人家的fan song給粉絲聽 是還嫌自己團不夠黑嗎？<br />\n噓 VIC0418: 剩下一年什麼都不怕啦，<br />\n噓 yiln10510: 臉皮真厚，造假C位<br />\n&rarr; jas0083: CJ操作完全跟隨對岸論壇小粉紅節奏走欸<br />\n噓 hoocheng: 這團體公司創作操作新聞超強強，後面再出來道歉，粉絲再說都道歉要怎樣<br />\n噓 giraffe03: fan song意義不知道嗎？撇開輩分不談，是特別給sone的歌，直接拿去借花獻佛？<br />\n噓 Corydoras: 作弊的第一名<br />\n噓 elyse0811: 人家有cj當靠山，沒在怕好嗎？<br />\n噓 ml0302: 重點是她唱了別家的fan song<br />\n噓 JingP: 那麼多歌可以唱 偏偏挑別人珍貴的的fan song<br />\n噓 ssss06: 臉皮到底可以多厚...<br />\n噓 BunnyBerry22: 自己的黑點自己造 看能不能黑到發亮<br />\n噓 emissary: 為什麼要用少時9週年紀念歌，自己寫好嗎<br />\n噓 wellnoshade: 不是SONE但忍不住要噓。已經有造假風波本應低調，結果還動人家的fan song，是故意的話也太惡劣，是大意的話也太笨。<br />\n噓 tieneun: 只能用別人針對他們來安慰自己啊<br />\n噓 VIC0418: 這團粉絲真的奇葩，趕快解散吧根本毒瘤<br />\n噓 VIC0418: 這團粉絲有認錯過嗎？都是別人的錯？"},{"pid":"5084a1233d7d862bf1cd4a06ca8eb8c2cb8ac7c4","tid":1884861,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"c3359a8d7c28dbeb92d9eb252f85fda38537ed86","tid":1884861,"uid":555,"like":16,"dislike":34,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"sone麻撚煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"YES<